---
title: Herby Chicken & Garlic Greens with Dill & Parsley Mayo
description: Dive into this spectacular dish. Chicken is perfectly seared for a crispy, golden finish, then paired with garlicky greens that pack a punch. Dip each bite into the creamy dill-parsley mayo for a fresh, herby twist - it’s a flavour combo that’ll keep you coming back for more!

